                                        ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን።
                                        </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus target="#267v"/>
                                    <desc type="Inventory">Inventory of books belonging to the church of <placeName ref="INS0450QahaI"/>
